    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh alright. if I do decide to just try the RICE thing and some ibuprofen for like 3 or 4 days first, is there anything else i can do at home to make sure it's not getting worse? like a specific way to wrap it or something? i'm just really hoping i can avoid the doctor if i can help it.",
